---
title: Mediterranean Bacon & Pumpkin Risotto with Baby Leaves, Parmesan & Almonds
description: This rich pumpkin risotto comes together in the oven, leaving you to kick your feet up and enjoy quality time with the ones who matter. With a flavourful chargrilled capsicum relish stirred through and and a sprinkle of flaked almonds on top, this Mediterranean pork delight is a must-have meal!

